<div class="contents">

<p>This class is responsible for application discovering in the autodeploy dir and for any method associated with loading and unload applications. This class should maintain the list of opened applications, should be smart enough to create a process for each application and to serve as a "watchdog" for applications that crash and should be restarted if possible.  
<a href="#details">More...</a></p>

